data.description: Highly sought-after Parkview High School District, this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath gem is not just a home. Perfectly situated for an effortless blend of modern living and easy access to everyday essentials. Step inside to the spacious open living room featuring a charming fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for cozy family gatherings or entertaining friends. The high ceilings add an airy feel. The eat-in kitchen has an abundance of cabinets and pantry space. Convenience is key, and this home delivers! The Primary bedroom on the main floor provides flexibility, while large secondary bedrooms and an additional bonus room upstairs offer endless possibilities. Whether it's a home office, a playroom, or a guest suite, the choice is yours! Updated with new LVP flooring, this home seamlessly blends style and functionality. Low HOA ensures your budget stays on track while allowing you to enjoy the perks of a well-maintained community. Conveniently situated with easy access to shopping centers, entertainment and recreation you'll never be far from life's necessities.
